Notice:
	temp and cache dir should be in the same partition so that files can be moved fast.

Dependency:
	gearman
	memcache
	mplayer
	mencoder (component of mplayer)
	ffmpeg
	yamdi (Windows version in distfile/)
	ImageMagick
	7-zip
	flowplayer
	LibreOffice or OpenOffice.org
	unoconv (can be run by python bundled in OOo)
	ghostscript
	firefox 2+
	Pearl Crescent Page Saver (Basic)

Other:
	"C:/OpenOffice.org/program/soffice.exe" -headless -norestore -accept="socket,host=localhost,port=2002;urp;"
